name: 2021 4+ Supporters
description:
As my final mint for 2021, I wanted to recognize not only my collectors but those who went the extra mile and collected 4 or more of my pieces. 

From the 163 Collectors, 22 people held that status.

I want to thank you all for the support and encouragement. I've really felt like I was part of a community and I've really enjoyed the company on this artistic journey.

Here's to 2021 and all the best, as we continue the journey in 2022!
